[챠트조회]SELECT P.PATID as 챠트번호, P.PATNAME as 이름, P.SEX, O.ACPTDATE as 접수일자, O.ACPTSEQ, O.RSVACPTSTATE, O.RESULTSTATE, O.DEPTCODE, O.ORDERDATE, O.SLIPNO, O.IOFLAG, O.ORDERCODE, O.ORDERNAME, R.SPCMNO as 바코드번호, R.RESULTFLAG, R.RESULTNO, R.RESULTITEMCODE as ITEM   FROM registinfos O, resultofnum R, PATMST P  WHERE O.acptdate = R.acptdate    AND O.acptdate between '20170323' and '20170327'   AND P.PATID = 'lypo 1'   AND R.resultitemcode in ('XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0029','XC0021','XC0022','XC00038','XC00301','XC0030','XC0025','XC0047','XC0034','XC0031','XC0032','XC0037','XC0048','XC0049','XC0055','LC000137','XC0060','XC0063','XC0064','XC0035','LC1481','XC0062','XC0057','XC0080','XC100801','XC1008','XI0015','XI0016','XC0056','XC0049','XC00221','LC121','XC00222','LC0005','LC0004')   AND O.patid = R.patid    AND O.acptseq = R.acptseq    AND O.patid = P.patid    AND O.CLAS = 4    AND R.RESULTFLAG = 0    AND O.rsvacptstate < '5' 
[챠트조회-Ret]

[챠트조회]SELECT P.PATID as 챠트번호, P.PATNAME as 이름, P.SEX, O.ACPTDATE as 접수일자, O.ACPTSEQ, O.RSVACPTSTATE, O.RESULTSTATE, O.DEPTCODE, O.ORDERDATE, O.SLIPNO, O.IOFLAG, O.ORDERCODE, O.ORDERNAME, R.SPCMNO as 바코드번호, R.RESULTFLAG, R.RESULTNO, R.RESULTITEMCODE as ITEM   FROM registinfos O, resultofnum R, PATMST P  WHERE O.acptdate = R.acptdate    AND O.acptdate between '20170323' and '20170327'   AND P.PATID = 'lypo 2'   AND R.resultitemcode in ('XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0029','XC0021','XC0022','XC00038','XC00301','XC0030','XC0025','XC0047','XC0034','XC0031','XC0032','XC0037','XC0048','XC0049','XC0055','LC000137','XC0060','XC0063','XC0064','XC0035','LC1481','XC0062','XC0057','XC0080','XC100801','XC1008','XI0015','XI0016','XC0056','XC0049','XC00221','LC121','XC00222','LC0005','LC0004')   AND O.patid = R.patid    AND O.acptseq = R.acptseq    AND O.patid = P.patid    AND O.CLAS = 4    AND R.RESULTFLAG = 0    AND O.rsvacptstate < '5' 
[챠트조회-Ret]
[DELETE]DELETE FROM PATRESULT 
 WHERE mid(EXAMDATE,1,8) = '20170327' 
   AND EQUIPNO = 'H7100' 
   AND SAVESEQ = 2
   AND BARCODE = '' 
   AND EQUIPCODE = '1'
   AND EXAMCODE = 'XC0027'

[챠트조회]SELECT P.PATID as 챠트번호, P.PATNAME as 이름, P.SEX, O.ACPTDATE as 접수일자, O.ACPTSEQ, O.RSVACPTSTATE, O.RESULTSTATE, O.DEPTCODE, O.ORDERDATE, O.SLIPNO, O.IOFLAG, O.ORDERCODE, O.ORDERNAME, R.SPCMNO as 바코드번호, R.RESULTFLAG, R.RESULTNO, R.RESULTITEMCODE as ITEM   FROM registinfos O, resultofnum R, PATMST P  WHERE O.acptdate = R.acptdate    AND O.acptdate between '20170323' and '20170327'   AND P.PATID = '00056724'   AND R.resultitemcode in ('XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0029','XC0021','XC0022','XC00038','XC00301','XC0030','XC0025','XC0047','XC0034','XC0031','XC0032','XC0037','XC0048','XC0049','XC0055','LC000137','XC0060','XC0063','XC0064','XC0035','LC1481','XC0062','XC0057','XC0080','XC100801','XC1008','XI0015','XI0016','XC0056','XC0049','XC00221','LC121','XC00222','LC0005','LC0004')   AND O.patid = R.patid    AND O.acptseq = R.acptseq    AND O.patid = P.patid    AND O.CLAS = 4    AND R.RESULTFLAG = 0    AND O.rsvacptstate < '5'

[INSERT]INSERT INTO PATRESULT (
SAVESEQ, EXAMDATE, HOSPDATE, EQUIPNO, BARCODE

[챠트조회]SELECT P.PATID as 챠트번호, P.PATNAME as 이름, P.SEX, O.ACPTDATE as 접수일자, O.ACPTSEQ, O.RSVACPTSTATE, O.RESULTSTATE, O.DEPTCODE, O.ORDERDATE, O.SLIPNO, O.IOFLAG, O.ORDERCODE, O.ORDERNAME, R.SPCMNO as 바코드번호, R.RESULTFLAG, R.RESULTNO, R.RESULTITEMCODE as ITEM   FROM registinfos O, resultofnum R, PATMST P  WHERE O.acptdate = R.acptdate    AND O.acptdate between '20170323' and '20170327'   AND P.PATID = '00138051'   AND R.resultitemcode in ('XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0029','XC0021','XC0022','XC00038','XC00301','XC0030','XC0025','XC0047','XC0034','XC0031','XC0032','XC0037','XC0048','XC0049','XC0055','LC000137','XC0060','XC0063','XC0064','XC0035','LC1481','XC0062','XC0057','XC0080','XC100801','XC1008','XI0015','XI0016','XC0056','XC0049','XC00221','LC121','XC00222','LC0005','LC0004')   AND O.patid = R.patid    AND O.acptseq = R.acptseq    AND O.patid = P.patid    AND O.CLAS = 4    AND R.RESULTFLAG = 0    AND O.rsvacptstate < '5'

[챠트조회]SELECT P.PATID as 챠트번호, P.PATNAME as 이름, P.SEX, O.ACPTDATE as 접수일자, O.ACPTSEQ, O.RSVACPTSTATE, O.RESULTSTATE, O.DEPTCODE, O.ORDERDATE, O.SLIPNO, O.IOFLAG, O.ORDERCODE, O.ORDERNAME, R.SPCMNO as 바코드번호, R.RESULTFLAG, R.RESULTNO, R.RESULTITEMCODE as ITEM   FROM registinfos O, resultofnum R, PATMST P  WHERE O.acptdate = R.acptdate    AND O.acptdate between '20170323' and '20170327'   AND P.PATID = '00109415'   AND R.resultitemcode in ('XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0029','XC0021','XC0022','XC00038','XC00301','XC0030','XC0025','XC0047','XC0034','XC0031','XC0032','XC0037','XC0048','XC0049','XC0055','LC000137','XC0060','XC0063','XC0064','XC0035','LC1481','XC0062','XC0057','XC0080','XC100801','XC1008','XI0015','XI0016','XC0056','XC0049','XC00221','LC121','XC00222','LC0005','LC0004')   AND O.patid = R.patid    AND O.acptseq = R.acptseq    AND O.patid = P.patid    AND O.CLAS = 4    AND R.RESULTFLAG = 0    AND O.rsvacptstate < '5'

[챠트조회]SELECT P.PATID as 챠트번호, P.PATNAME as 이름, P.SEX, O.ACPTDATE as 접수일자, O.ACPTSEQ, O.RSVACPTSTATE, O.RESULTSTATE, O.DEPTCODE, O.ORDERDATE, O.SLIPNO, O.IOFLAG, O.ORDERCODE, O.ORDERNAME, R.SPCMNO as 바코드번호, R.RESULTFLAG, R.RESULTNO, R.RESULTITEMCODE as ITEM   FROM registinfos O, resultofnum R, PATMST P  WHERE O.acptdate = R.acptdate    AND O.acptdate between '20170323' and '20170327'   AND P.PATID = '00036221'   AND R.resultitemcode in ('XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0029','XC0021','XC0022','XC00038','XC00301','XC0030','XC0025','XC0047','XC0034','XC0031','XC0032','XC0037','XC0048','XC0049','XC0055','LC000137','XC0060','XC0063','XC0064','XC0035','LC1481','XC0062','XC0057','XC0080','XC100801','XC1008','XI0015','XI0016','XC0056','XC0049','XC00221','LC121','XC00222','LC0005','LC0004')   AND O.patid = R.patid    AND O.acptseq = R.acptseq    AND O.patid = P.patid    AND O.CLAS = 4    AND R.RESULTFLAG = 0    AND O.rsvacptstate < '5' 
[챠트조회-Ret]'XC0030','XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0032','XC0025','XC0048','XC0049','XC0047'

[바코드조회]SELECT P.PATID as 챠트번호, P.PATNAME as 이름, P.SEX, O.ACPTDATE as 접수일자, O.ACPTSEQ, O.RSVACPTSTATE, O.RESULTSTATE, O.DEPTCODE, O.ORDERDATE, O.SLIPNO, O.IOFLAG, O.ORDERCODE, O.ORDERNAME, R.SPCMNO as 바코드번호, R.RESULTFLAG, R.RESULTNO, R.RESULTITEMCODE as ITEM   FROM registinfos O, resultofnum R, PATMST P  WHERE O.acptdate = R.acptdate    AND R.SPCMNO = '1703250077'   AND R.resultitemcode in ('XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0029','XC0021','XC0022','XC00038','XC00301','XC0030','XC0025','XC0047','XC0034','XC0031','XC0032','XC0037','XC0048','XC0049','XC0055','LC000137','XC0060','XC0063','XC0064','XC0035','LC1481','XC0062','XC0057','XC0080','XC100801','XC1008','XI0015','XI0016','XC0056','XC0049','XC00221','LC121','XC00222','LC0005','LC0004')   AND O.patid = R.patid    AND O.acptseq = R.acptseq    AND O.patid = P.patid    AND O.CLAS = 4    AND R.RESULTFLAG = 0    AND O.rsvacptstate < '5'

[바코드조회]SELECT P.PATID as 챠트번호, P.PATNAME as 이름, P.SEX, O.ACPTDATE as 접수일자, O.ACPTSEQ, O.RSVACPTSTATE, O.RESULTSTATE, O.DEPTCODE, O.ORDERDATE, O.SLIPNO, O.IOFLAG, O.ORDERCODE, O.ORDERNAME, R.SPCMNO as 바코드번호, R.RESULTFLAG, R.RESULTNO, R.RESULTITEMCODE as ITEM   FROM registinfos O, resultofnum R, PATMST P  WHERE O.acptdate = R.acptdate    AND R.SPCMNO = '1703250064'   AND R.resultitemcode in ('XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0029','XC0021','XC0022','XC00038','XC00301','XC0030','XC0025','XC0047','XC0034','XC0031','XC0032','XC0037','XC0048','XC0049','XC0055','LC000137','XC0060','XC0063','XC0064','XC0035','LC1481','XC0062','XC0057','XC0080','XC100801','XC1008','XI0015','XI0016','XC0056','XC0049','XC00221','LC121','XC00222','LC0005','LC0004')   AND O.patid = R.patid    AND O.acptseq = R.acptseq    AND O.patid = P.patid    AND O.CLAS = 4    AND R.RESULTFLAG = 0    AND O.rsvacptstate < '5'

[참고치]Select REFHIGHVAL,REFLOWVAL    From RESULTOFNUM  Where PATID = '00139838'   And ACPTDATE = '20170327'    And RESULTITEMCODE = 'XC0027'   AND CLAS = '4'

[바코드조회]SELECT P.PATID as 챠트번호, P.PATNAME as 이름, P.SEX, O.ACPTDATE as 접수일자, O.ACPTSEQ, O.RSVACPTSTATE, O.RESULTSTATE, O.DEPTCODE, O.ORDERDATE, O.SLIPNO, O.IOFLAG, O.ORDERCODE, O.ORDERNAME, R.SPCMNO as 바코드번호, R.RESULTFLAG, R.RESULTNO, R.RESULTITEMCODE as ITEM   FROM registinfos O, resultofnum R, PATMST P  WHERE O.acptdate = R.acptdate    AND R.SPCMNO = '1703270141'   AND R.resultitemcode in ('XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0029','XC0021','XC0022','XC00038','XC00301','XC0030','XC0025','XC0047','XC0034','XC0031','XC0032','XC0037','XC0048','XC0049','XC0055','LC000137','XC0060','XC0063','XC0064','XC0035','LC1481','XC0062','XC0057','XC0080','XC100801','XC1008','XI0015','XI0016','XC0056','XC0049','XC00221','LC121','XC00222','LC0005','LC0004')   AND O.patid = R.patid    AND O.acptseq = R.acptseq    AND O.patid = P.patid    AND O.CLAS = 4    AND R.RESULTFLAG = 0    AND O.rsvacptstate < '5' 
[바코드조회-Ret]'XC0080','XC0037'
[SQL]UPDATE PATRESULT SET HOSPDATE = '20170327'

[바코드조회]SELECT P.PATID as 챠트번호, P.PATNAME as 이름, P.SEX, O.ACPTDATE as 접수일자, O.ACPTSEQ, O.RSVACPTSTATE, O.RESULTSTATE, O.DEPTCODE, O.ORDERDATE, O.SLIPNO, O.IOFLAG, O.ORDERCODE, O.ORDERNAME, R.SPCMNO as 바코드번호, R.RESULTFLAG, R.RESULTNO, R.RESULTITEMCODE as ITEM   FROM registinfos O, resultofnum R, PATMST P  WHERE O.acptdate = R.acptdate    AND R.SPCMNO = '1703270064'   AND R.resultitemcode in ('XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0029','XC0021','XC0022','XC00038','XC00301','XC0030','XC0025','XC0047','XC0034','XC0031','XC0032','XC0037','XC0048','XC0049','XC0055','LC000137','XC0060','XC0063','XC0064','XC0035','LC1481','XC0062','XC0057','XC0080','XC100801','XC1008','XI0015','XI0016','XC0056','XC0049','XC00221','LC121','XC00222','LC0005','LC0004')   AND O.patid = R.patid    AND O.acptseq = R.acptseq    AND O.patid = P.patid    AND O.CLAS = 4    AND R.RESULTFLAG = 0    AND O.rsvacptstate < '5'

[SQL]UPDATE PATRESULT SET HOSPDATE = '20170327' 
,BARCODE = '1703270064' 
,CHARTNO = '00119635' 
,PID = '' 
,PNAME = '강재건' 
,INOUT = '' 
,PSEX = '' 
,PAGE = '' 
 WHERE EQUIPNO = 'H7100' 
   AND SAVESEQ = 48

  FROM PATRESULT 
 WHERE EQUIPNO = 'H7100' 
   AND MID(EXAMDATE,1,8) = '20170327'  
   AND BARCODE = '1703270055' 
   AND SAVESEQ = 45

[결과저장] Update resultofnum Set resultindate = to_char(sysdate,'yyyymmdd') , resultintime = to_char(sysdate,'HH24MI') , resultinid = 'HM병원' , resultflag = '1'  , highlowflag = ''  , textresultval= '5.4' , NUMRESULTVAL = '5.4' where spcmno = '1703270055' and resultitemcode = 'XC0080' and resultflag < '2'

[바코드조회]SELECT P.PATID as 챠트번호, P.PATNAME as 이름, P.SEX, O.ACPTDATE as 접수일자, O.ACPTSEQ, O.RSVACPTSTATE, O.RESULTSTATE, O.DEPTCODE, O.ORDERDATE, O.SLIPNO, O.IOFLAG, O.ORDERCODE, O.ORDERNAME, R.SPCMNO as 바코드번호, R.RESULTFLAG, R.RESULTNO, R.RESULTITEMCODE as ITEM   FROM registinfos O, resultofnum R, PATMST P  WHERE O.acptdate = R.acptdate    AND R.SPCMNO = '1703270099'   AND R.resultitemcode in ('XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0029','XC0021','XC0022','XC00038','XC00301','XC0030','XC0025','XC0047','XC0034','XC0031','XC0032','XC0037','XC0048','XC0049','XC0055','LC000137','XC0060','XC0063','XC0064','XC0035','LC1481','XC0062','XC0057','XC0080','XC100801','XC1008','XI0015','XI0016','XC0056','XC0049','XC00221','LC121','XC00222','LC0005','LC0004')   AND O.patid = R.patid    AND O.acptseq = R.acptseq    AND O.patid = P.patid    AND O.CLAS = 4    AND R.RESULTFLAG = 0    AND O.rsvacptstate < '5' 
[바코드조회-Ret]'XC0030','XC0027','XC0028','XC0038','XC0032','XC0025','XC0048','XC0049','XC0047'
